{
  "texts": [
    "C. Setup and ParticipantsThe study was conducted fully in-person using the same setup: a 2020 Macbook Mini attached to a 27-inch display.",
    "Both user interfaces were accessed through the Firefox browser.",
    "The Google doc for drafting the literature review outline is in a Chrome browser for easy switching.",
    "All participants used the Macbook Mini's trackpad and keyboard for interaction.",
    "Before the literature review task began, we provided enough time for participants to get familiar with the trackpad and keyboard.A total of 12 (6 for each group) participants were recruited."
  ]
}